" Shortcut to type panorama in the command line
cnoremap <C-p> panorama<Space>switch<Space>

" I forget, beep at me if I try to go back while typing text?
inoremap <C-o> <Esc>:beep<Return>

" Ctrl a selects all instead of going to beginning of line
inoremap <C-a> <Insert><C-a><Insert>

" F9 shows the tab to the left while in insert mode
inoremap <F9> <Esc>:bNext<Return>

" F12 shows the tab to the right while in insert mode
inoremap <F12> <Esc>:bnext<Return>

" F9 shows the tab to the left
noremap <F9> :bNext<Return>

" F12 shows the tab to the right
noremap <F12> :bnext<Return>

" Toggle permanently allow site in noscript
noremap <A-S-s> :noscript toggleperm

" Toggle temporarily allow in noscript
noremap <A-s> :noscript toggletemp

" Open downloads in freecommander
noremap <A-d> :silent<Space>run<Space>c:\PROGRA~2\FREECO~1\FreeCommander.exe<Space>/c<Space>d:\downloads<Return>

" Map x to search the firefox menu items
noremap x :emenu<Space>

" Shift c closes the active window- because extension "minimize on start and close"
noremap C :winclose<Return>

" move cmdline to downloads
noremap <C-S-d> :cd d:\downloads<CR>

" Ctrl shift p opens a private window
noremap <C-S-P> :winopen<Space>-private<Return>

" Ctrl ] saves the current url using wget (to the current cmdline directory) and closes the tab
noremap <C-]> O<Home><C-Del>!c:\cygwin64\bin\wget<Space>--no-check-certificate<Space><Return>qd

" Ctrl [ opens up a cmdline ready to save the current url to the cmdline directory- type a filename
noremap <C-[> O<Home><C-Del>!c:\cygwin64\bin\wget<Space>--no-check-certificate<Space>-O<Space><Space><Left>

" Toggle show/hide tabs with ctrl t
noremap <C-t> :set<Space>toolbars+=tabs,notabs<Return>

" Toggle show/hide address bar with ctrl shift t
noremap <C-S-t> :set<Space>toolbars+=navigation,nonavigation<Return>

" Open a cmdline preconfigured to search the current tab's site.
noremap <C-A-s> O<Home><Right><Right><Right><Right><Right>site:<Left><Left><Left><Left><Left><Left><Space>

" Show all tabs in current window via firefox thing
noremap s :emenu<Space>View.Show<Space>All<Space>Tabs<Return>

" Let firefox handle tab closes with the d key- vimperator always shows the tab to the left instead of last viewed tab
noremap d <C-w>

" Open a cmdline ready to mux youtube (or any) audio and video streams into one file
noremap <C-0> :!C:\Progra~1\MediaCoder\codecs64\ffmpeg.exe -i input_video.mp4 -i input_audio.m4a -acodec copy -vcodec copy outfile.mp4

" Yank site url and title
nnoremap Ya :js util.copyToClipboard(buffer.URL+String.fromCharCode(10)+buffer.title)

" Yank site title
nnoremap Yt :js util.copyToClipboard(buffer.title)

